data.name: Sample - Fortinet FortiAuthenticator - 1.0.0
data.description: Sample playbooks for "Fortinet FortiAuthenticator" connector. If you are planning to use any of the sample playbooks in your environment, ensure that you clone those playbooks and move them to a different collection, since the sample playbook collection gets deleted during connector upgrade and delete.
